    <div class="additional-page-lazy">
        <h4 class="mb-2 mt-3 content-title">Lazy loading</h4>
        <p class="mb-2 mt-3 article-content">If you want to add some delay when router is loading add lazy array objects in <b>routerConfig.js</b> configuration</p>
<pre>
<code class="hljs javascript">
    lazy: {
        loading: true
    },
</code>
</pre>
        <p class="article-content">By default lazy loading is set to true and has additional 500 milliseconds.</p>
        <p class="article-content">If you want to set custom delay interval, set duration object into lazy array.</p>
<pre>
<code class="hljs javascript">
    lazy: {
        loading: true,
        duration: 1000 // in milliseconds
    },
</code>
</pre>
